response.original_title: Spacey Jane - Live in Melbourne from Reunion Park
response.overview: Recorded on March 19, 2022, at Reunion Park, an open-air pop-up venue in Melbourne, Australia, this set captures the Perth indie-rock band's headline show during the pre-release tour for their album Here Comes Everybody.  A setlist is not officially published, but the performance included around 15 tracks, featuring singles and fan favorites from Here Comes Everybody and earlier releases.  This 45–60 minute concert reflects the band’s shift from raw garage-indie to a more polished, melodic sound, aligning with their rising profile in Australia. The full concert film is publicly available to stream on YouTube with accompanying pro-shot footage .
response.title: Spacey Jane - Live in Melbourne from Reunion Park
